hen":174,"who":158},"Jonathan Prag added pilot bilingualism annotation","2024-09-24",{"n":86,"url":87,"height":88,"width":89,"desc":90,"surfaceType":91},[],[178,179,180,181],"Ferrara, 1829, Storia di Catania sino alla fine del secolo XVIII","Kaibel, 1890, IG","Boeckh, Franz, 1853, CIG","Korhonen, 2004, La cultura epigrafica della colonia di Catina nell'alto impero",[183,184,185,186],"82T4IWDN","Q2SBPG9F","TQMVHEVL","NMS48IZF",[188,189,190,22,26,191,192,193,194,192,195,95],"isic001307","i.sicily inscription 001307",{"_":5},"catina","catania","sicilia","sicily","latin and ancient greek",[],{"title":198,"body":199,"divs":200,"editions":225,"images":235,"handnote":241},"ISic001307. I.Sicily inscription 001307","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">D(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) ·\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδία Βαλεντεῖνα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\">Κλωδία\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βαλεντεῖνα\">Βαλεντεῖνα\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>χαῖρε ἔζη(σεν) ἔ(τη) \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">XXXX\u003C/span>´ \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ἐποίησε ἰδίᾳ γυναι-\u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>κὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰγνᾶτις Κάρικος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰγνᾶτις\">Ἰγνᾶτις\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κάρικος\">Κάρικος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>μνή(μης) χάριν \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">D·M·S·\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδία Βαλεντεῖνα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βαλεντεῖνα\">ΒΑΛΕΝΤΕΙΝΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΧΑΙΡΕΕΖΗΕ\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">XXXX\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΙΔΙΑΓΥΝΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΚΙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰγνᾶτις Κάρικος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰγνᾶτις\">ΙΓΝΑΤΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κάρικος\">ΚΑΡΙΚΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΜΝΗΧΑΡΙΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001307_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001307_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001307.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001307-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Kaibel in IG\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. Klodia Balenteina, farewell. She lived 40 years. Ignatis Karikos made this for his own wife, for the sake of her memory.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text is distinctive for a number of features illustrating linguistic interference from Latin: the use of the Latin abbreviated header DMS (with interpuncts according to the transcriptions, not used in the rest of the text); the use of Latin numerals in line 3; the use of abbreviations both for \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἔζη(σεν) ἔ(τη)\u003C/span> and \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μνή(μης) χάριν\u003C/span>. The unusual structure of the text (and use of χαῖρε which is not generally attested at Catania) further marks it out as distinctive, and Korhonen emphasises its extra-urban provenance.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 387 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Franz 1853 5396 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">484\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 249 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001897\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001897\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[201,204,207,210,213,216,219,222],{"id":202,"html":203},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">D(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) ·\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδία Βαλεντεῖνα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\">Κλωδία\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βαλεντεῖνα\">Βαλεντεῖνα\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>χαῖρε ἔζη(σεν) ἔ(τη) \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">XXXX\u003C/span>´ \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ἐποίησε ἰδίᾳ γυναι-\u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>κὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data